rk — subject must match its title.'=>'Send a new version of an existing artwork — subject must match its title.','Request an existing artwork or event be taken down — subject must match its title.'=>'Request an existing artwork or event be taken down — subject must match its title.','Promote'=>'Promote','Choose which artwork represents you in the shared community gallery on the main site — subject must match its title. Your own subdomain already shows everything you\'ve published.'=>'Choose which artwork represents you in the shared community gallery on the main site — subject must match its title. Your own subdomain already shows everything you\'ve published.','Photo-only'=>'Photo-only','Publish a photo exactly as sent — no AI enhancement, no quality check.'=>'Publish a photo exactly as sent — no AI enhancement, no quality check.','Pure'=>'Pure','Publish exactly as sent — no AI at all, not even the title/description pass.'=>'Publish exactly as sent — no AI at all, not even the title/description pass.','Send a message to every other artist in the community.'=>'Send a message to every other artist in the community.','Spotted something to fix after publishing? Log in and look for the pencil icon on your published page — you can correct the title, text, or photo yourself, no need to email us again.'=>'Spotted something to fix after publishing? Log in and look for the pencil icon on your published page — you can correct the title, text, or photo yourself, no need to email us again.','Manage notification preferences: %s'=>'Manage notification preferences: %s','Manage notification preferences'=>'Manage notification preferences','Agnosis Membership Application'=>'Agnosis Membership Application','Agnosis Governance Participation'=>'Agnosis Governance Participation','Agnosis Newsletter Subscription'=>'Agnosis Newsletter Subscription','Agnosis Newsletter Delivery History'=>'Agnosis Newsletter Delivery History','Agnosis Contact Messages Sent'=>'Agnosis Contact Messages Sent','Agnosis Transactions'=>'Agnosis Transactions','Agnosis Notification Preferences'=>'Agnosis Notification Preferences','Display name'=>'Display name','Application statement'=>'Application statement','Language'=>'Language','Applied at'=>'Applied at','Resolved at'=>'Resolved at','Type'=>'Type','Community vouch given'=>'Community vouch given','Date'=>'Date','Admission vouch given'=>'Admission vouch given','Community removal vote'=>'Community removal vote','Vote'=>'Vote','Community size-cap vote'=>'Community size-cap vote','Locale'=>'Locale','Subscribed at'=>'Subscribed at','Confirmed at'=>'Confirmed at','Unsubscribed at'=>'Unsubscribed at','Issue'=>'Issue','Recipient type'=>'Recipient type','Queued at'=>'Queued at','Sent to artist'=>'Sent to artist','Translated message'=>'Translated message','Rejection reason'=>'Rejection reason','IP address'=>'IP address','Sent at'=>'Sent at','Amount'=>'Amount','Currency'=>'Currency','Fee'=>'Fee','Gateway'=>'Gateway','Your membership application/account is still active. To remove this data, use the "leave the network" link from any Agnosis email, or ask an administrator.'=>'Your membership application/account is still active. To remove this data, use the "leave the network" link from any Agnosis email, or ask an administrator.','Your biography, statement, and portfolio link were erased. Your email address was kept on file — your account is currently banned, and it\'s the only way this site can continue to enforce that.'=>'Your biography, statement, and portfolio link were erased. Your email address was kept on file — your account is currently banned, and it\'s the only way this site can continue to enforce that.','[message removed]'=>'[message removed]','Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it would silently change a settled decision.'=>'Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it would silently change a settled decision.','Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts were kept for statistics.'=>'Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts were kept for statistics.','Transaction (donation/sale) records were kept in full — financial records are subject to a legal retention obligation and are exempt from erasure under GDPR Art. 17(3)(b).'=>'Transaction (donation/sale) records were kept in full — financial records are subject to a legal retention obligation and are exempt from erasure under GDPR Art. 17(3)(b).','Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site\'s actual configuration before publishing.'=>'Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site\'s actual configuration before publishing.','What personal data we collect and why'=>'What personal data we collect and why','When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues.'=>'When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues.','Who we share it with'=>'Who we share it with','Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site\'s configuration) to help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses WordPress\'s own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the Fediverse) as part of this plugin\'s core federation feature.'=>'Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site\'s configuration) to help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses WordPress\'s own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the Fediverse) as part of this plugin\'s core federation feature.','How long we retain your data'=>'How long we retain your data','Retention varies by data type; see this site\'s administrator for specifics. You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described above at any time using this site\'s standard WordPress data request tools.'=>'Retention varies by data type; see this site\'s administrator for specifics. You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described above at any time using this site\'s standard WordPress data request tools.','Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this cannot be fully undone later.'=>'Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this cannot be fully undone later.','Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being sent to the artist.'=>'Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being sent to the artist.','See our %s for details.'=>'See our %s for details.','Privacy Policy'=>'Privacy Policy','Too many requests. Please wait %d seconds and try again.'=>'Too many requests. Please wait %d seconds and try again.','Submission limit reached. Please wait before sending again.'=>'Submission limit reached. Please wait before sending again.','Please complete the verification check and try again.'=>'Please complete the verification check and try again.','Could not verify you\'re human right now. Please try again in a moment.'=>'Could not verify you\'re human right now. Please try again in a moment.','Verification failed. Please try again.'=>'Verification failed. Please try again.','View Agnosis details'=>'Agnosis Artist','View details'=>'View Event','Every 5 minutes'=>'Every 5 minutes','IMAP credentials are not configured.'=>'IMAP credentials are not configured.','Connected successfully. %1$d message(s) in inbox, %2$d unseen.'=>'Connected successfully. %1$d message(s) in inbox, %2$d unseen.','Webhook secret not configured.'=>'Webhook secret not configured.','Invalid or missing webhook signature.'=>'Invalid or missing webhook signature.','Webhook request timestamp is missing, malformed, or too old.'=>'Webhook request timestamp is missing, malformed, or too old.','This webhook request has already been processed.'=>'This webhook request has already been processed.','OpenSSL is required for HTTP Signature verification.'=>'OpenSSL is required for HTTP Signature verification.','Signature header is required.'=>'Signature header is required.','Signature header is missing required fields (keyId, headers, signature).'=>'Signature header is missing required fields (keyId, headers, signature).','Request date is too old or too far in the future.'=>'Request date is too old or too far in the future.','Signature value is not valid base64.'=>'Signature value is not valid base64.','HTTP Signature verification failed.'=>'HTTP Signature verification failed.','Digest header does not match the request body.'=>'Digest header does not match the request body.','keyId in Signature header is not a valid URL.'=>'keyId in Signature header is not a valid URL.','Failed to fetch actor document.'=>'Failed to fetch actor document.','Actor document returned a non-200 response.'=>'Actor document returned a non-200 response.','Actor document does not contain a publicKey.publicKeyPem field.'=>'Actor document does not contain a publicKey.publicKeyPem field.','Node URL is required.'=>'Node URL is required.','Contact %s'=>'Contact %s','Contact this artist'=>'Contact this artist','Get in touch with %s'=>'Get in touch with %s','Get in touch'=>'Get in touch','This newsletter issue could not be found.'=>'This newsletter issue could not be found.','Issue not found'=>'Issue not found','Newsletter archive'=>'Newsletter archive','Past issues of the %s newsletter.'=>'Past issues of the %s newsletter.','No issues have gone out yet — check back soon.'=>'No issues have gone out yet — check back soon.','← Newer'=>'← Newer','Older →'=>'Older →','Newsletter archive — %s'=>'Newsletter archive — %s','%1$s Newsletter — %2$s'=>'%1$s Newsletter — %2$s','%s Newsletter'=>'%s Newsletter','Nothing new to report this time — but the community is still here, and the next issue will have more.'=>'Nothing new to report this time — but the community is still here, and the next issue will have more.','New artwork'=>'New artwork','Upcoming events'=>'Upcoming events','%d new artwork published'=>'%d new artwork published' . "\0" . '%d new artworks published','%d new event announced'=>'%d new event announced' . "\0" . '%d new events announced','Welcome to our newest member: %s'=>'Welcome to our newest member: %s' . "\0" . '