", but couldn\'t find an artwork or event with that exact title in your account.'=>'We received a removal request for "%s", but couldn\'t find an artwork or event with that exact title in your account.','We received a request to feature "%s", but couldn\'t find a published artwork with that exact title in your account.'=>'We received a request to feature "%s", but couldn\'t find a published artwork with that exact title in your account.','Did you mean "%s"?'=>'Did you mean "%s"?','Yes, remove this instead'=>'Yes, remove this instead','Or simply resend your original email with that exact title.'=>'Or simply resend your original email with that exact title.','Resend your original email with that exact title.'=>'Resend your original email with that exact title.','Your current titles:'=>'Your current titles:','Titles are matched exactly, so a small difference in wording is enough to miss — double-check spelling, capitalization, and punctuation against the list above before resending.'=>'Titles are matched exactly, so a small difference in wording is enough to miss — double-check spelling, capitalization, and punctuation against the list above before resending.','"%s" is now your featured artwork on the gallery overview.'=>'"%s" is now your featured artwork on the gallery overview.','Any previously featured artwork has been unfeatured automatically — only one piece is featured at a time.'=>'Any previously featured artwork has been unfeatured automatically — only one piece is featured at a time.','[Agnosis] Your submission is ready to review: %s'=>'[Agnosis] Your submission is ready to review: %s','event'=>'event','artwork'=>'artwork','We received a removal request for the following %s:'=>'We received a removal request for the following %s:','If you want to permanently remove this %s, click the button below. This action cannot be undone.'=>'If you want to permanently remove this %s, click the button below. This action cannot be undone.','Yes, remove this %s'=>'Yes, remove this %s','If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — your %s will remain published.'=>'If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — your %s will remain published.','This confirmation link expires in 7 days.'=>'This confirmation link expires in 7 days.','If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — nothing will be removed unless you click one of the buttons above.'=>'If you did not request this removal, simply ignore this email — your %s will remain published.','These confirmation links expire in 7 days.'=>'This confirmation link expires in 7 days.','📷 Photo enhanced automatically'=>'📷 Photo enhanced automatically','We detected some photographic issues and applied AI correction to improve visibility of your artwork:'=>'We detected some photographic issues and applied AI correction to improve visibility of your artwork:','The artwork itself has not been altered — only the photograph quality was corrected.'=>'The artwork itself has not been altered — only the photograph quality was corrected.','📷 Photo quality score: %d/10'=>'📷 Photo quality score: %d/10','Double-check the link is correct — you can fix or remove it in the form below before publishing.'=>'Double-check the link is correct — you can fix or remove it in the form below before publishing.','If the link was correct, its destination may simply not be from a source this site automatically embeds.'=>'If the link was correct, its destination may simply not be from a source this site automatically embeds.','🔗 A link was not included'=>'🔗 A link was not included' . "\0" . '🔗 Some links were not included','The following couldn\'t be automatically embedded, so they were left out:'=>'The following couldn\'t be automatically embedded, so they were left out:','Its subject line didn\'t exactly match one of your existing titles. If you meant to update an existing event, "%s", resend your email with that exact title instead.'=>'Its subject line didn\'t exactly match one of your existing titles. If you meant to update an existing event, "%s", resend your email with that exact title instead.','Its subject line didn\'t exactly match one of your existing titles. If you meant to replace an existing artwork, "%s", resend your email with that exact title instead.'=>'Its subject line didn\'t exactly match one of your existing titles. If you meant to replace an existing artwork, "%s", resend your email with that exact title instead.','📄 This was published as a new post'=>'📄 This was published as a new post','Your submission has been processed. Here\'s what our AI curator came up with — take a look and let us know if it\'s ready to publish.'=>'Your submission has been processed. Here\'s what our AI curator came up with — take a look and let us know if it\'s ready to publish.','On the site: %s'=>'On the site: %s','In your language: %s'=>'In your language: %s','Looks great — Publish it'=>'Looks great — Publish it','Discard'=>'Discard','Want to tweak the title, text or tags before publishing?'=>'Want to tweak the title, text or tags before publishing?','Open your submissions page →'=>'Open your submissions page →','The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d day. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.'=>'The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d day. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.' . "\0" . 'The Publish and Discard links above expire in %d days. Your submission stays as a draft until you decide.','[%s] We couldn\'t process your submission'=>'[%s] We couldn\'t process your submission','[%s] We couldn\'t find a photo in your email'=>'[%s] We couldn\'t find a photo in your email','We received your email, but couldn\'t process a usable photo, audio, or video file from it — so nothing was published. This can happen when an image is pasted or inserted inline rather than added as a proper attachment, or when a file arrives in a format this server can\'t convert (for example, an iPhone photo saved in HEIC/HEIF format).'=>'We received your email, but couldn\'t process a usable photo, audio, or video file from it — so nothing was published. This can happen when an image is pasted or inserted inline rather than added as a proper attachment, or when a file arrives in a format this server can\'t convert (for example, an iPhone photo saved in HEIC/HEIF format).','To resend correctly:'=>'To resend correctly:','Use your mail app\'s "Attach file" (usually a paperclip icon) rather than "Insert photo" or pasting the image directly into the message body.'=>'Use your mail app\'s "Attach file" (usually a paperclip icon) rather than "Insert photo" or pasting the image directly into the message body.','If your photo was taken on an iPhone, try switching Settings → Camera → Formats to "Most Compatible" before taking or sending it, or use "Options" in Mail to send it as a JPEG.'=>'If your photo was taken on an iPhone, try switching Settings → Camera → Formats to "Most Compatible" before taking or sending it, or use "Options" in Mail to send it as a JPEG.','Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF, or HEIC/HEIF for images; MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG, or FLAC for audio; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG, or MPEG for video.'=>'Supported formats: JPEG, PNG, WebP, GIF, TIFF, or HEIC/HEIF for images; MP3, WAV, M4A, OGG, or FLAC for audio; MP4, MOV, AVI, WebM, OGG, or MPEG for video.','Once it\'s properly attached, just send it to the same address again — we\'ll pick it up automatically.'=>'Once it\'s properly attached, just send it to the same address again — we\'ll pick it up automatically.','[%s] We couldn\'t process that email'=>'[%s] We couldn\'t process your submission','Once it\'s a fresh, original message, just send it to the same address again — we\'ll pick it up automatically.'=>'Once it\'s properly attached, just send it to the same address again — we\'ll pick it up automatically.','The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.'=>'The photo is too dark to show your artwork clearly. Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.','The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.'=>'The photo is underexposed (too dark). Try photographing near a large window in daylight, or use a soft lamp aimed at the work from the side.','The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best.'=>'The photo is overexposed (too bright / washed out). Avoid direct sunlight or flash pointed straight at the artwork — diffuse or indirect light works best.','The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — diffuse light or shade gives more even tones.'=>'The photo is too bright or washed out. Avoid direct sunlight or flash — diffuse light or shade gives more even tones.','There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface.'=>'There is glare or a bright reflection on the artwork. Tilt the canvas slightly or photograph at an angle to eliminate reflections from the surface.','There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or change your angle to eliminate it.'=>'There is a reflection on the artwork surface. Tilt the canvas slightly or change your angle to eliminate it.','The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus locks on it.'=>'The image is blurry. Rest your phone or camera on a stable surface, use the self-timer, and make sure the artwork fills most of the frame so autofocus locks on it.','The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still.'=>'The image is out of focus. Tap on the artwork on your phone screen before shooting to make sure autofocus locks on it, and hold the camera still.','There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake.'=>'There is motion blur. Hold the camera very still or use a tripod; press the shutter gently or use the self-timer to avoid shake.','Camera shake is visible. Use a tripod or rest the camera on a flat surface and use the self-timer to avoid movement when pressing the shutter.'=>'Camera shake is visible. Use a tripod or rest the camera on a flat surface and use the self-timer to avoid movement when pressing the shutter.','The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and make sure you\'re close enough that the artwork fills the frame.'=>'The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and make sure you\'re close enough that the artwork fills the frame.','The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and fill the frame with the artwork.'=>'The image resolution is too low. Use your phone\'s highest quality setting and fill the frame with the artwork.','The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting on your camera.'=>'The image is pixelated. Shoot from closer or use a higher resolution setting on your camera.','The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your phone\'s Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors.'=>'The photo has a strong color cast. Shoot under neutral daylight or use your phone\'s Auto White Balance setting for more accurate colors.','The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch your phone\'s white balance to Daylight / Cloudy.'=>'The photo looks too yellow or warm. Shoot under natural daylight or switch your phone\'s white balance to Daylight / Cloudy.','The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural light source or adjust your camera\'s white balance.'=>'The photo has a cold blue tint. Move the artwork to a warmer, more natural light source or adjust your camera\'s white balance.','Part of the artwork appears to be cropped out of the frame. Step back and make sure the entire work is visible before shooting.'=>'Part of the artwork appears to be cropped out of the frame. Step back and make sure the entire work is visible before shooting.','The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight on, with the camera parallel to the canvas.'=>'The artwork is photographed at an angle, causing distortion. Shoot straight on, with the camera parallel to the canvas.','The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in front of the artwork, parallel to its surface.'=>'The artwork looks distorted or skewed. Position your camera directly in front of the artwork, parallel to its surface.','There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface.'=>'There is a shadow across part of the artwork. Reposition your light source or move the artwork so no shadows fall on the surface.','We received your submission, but unfortunately the photo quality is too low for us to show your artwork clearly. We didn\'t publish it — but please don\'t be discouraged! A simple retake is usually all it takes.'=>'We received your submission, but unfortunately the photo quality is too low for us to show your artwork clearly. We didn\'t publish it — but please don\'t be discouraged! A simple retake is usually all it takes.','📷 Photo quality score: %d / 10'=>'📷 Photo quality score: %d / 10','Here\'s what our AI detected and how to fix it:'=>'Here\'s what our AI detected and how to fix it:','The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork clearly.'=>'The overall photo quality was too low for our AI to process the artwork clearly.','💡 Quick tips for a great artwork photo'=>'💡 Quick tips for a great artwork photo','Use natural light — position the artwork near a window on a cloudy day for even, soft light.'=>'Use natural light — position the artwork near a window on a cloudy day for even, soft light.','Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid perspective distortion.'=>'Shoot straight on — hold your phone parallel to the canvas to avoid perspective distortion.','Fill the frame — let the artwork take up most of the shot; crop out distracting backgrounds.'=>'Fill the frame — let the artwork take up most of the shot; crop out distracting backgrounds.','Hold still — tap the artwork on your screen to focus, then press the shutter gently or use a self-timer.'=>'Hold still — tap the artwork on your screen to focus, then press the shutter gently or use a self-timer.','Once you have a clearer photo, just email it to the same address as before — we\'ll pick it up automatically.'=>'Once you have a clearer photo, just email it to the same address as before — we\'ll pick it up automatically.','Your previous submission is saved in your submissions page in case you want to review what was sent.'=>'Your previous submission is saved in your submissions page in case you want to review what was sent.','View submissions →'=>'View submissions →','Photo'=>'Photo','%s (original)'=>'%s (original)','%s (poster frame)'=>'%s (poster frame)','Failed to insert attachment.'=>'Failed to insert attachment.','Artwork or event not found.'=>'Artwork or event not found.','%s already removed.'=>'%s already removed.','Could not remove the %s. Please try again.'=>'Could not remove the %s. Please try again.','Your %s has been removed.'=>'Your %s has been removed.','A valid removal token is required.'=>'A valid removal token is required.','No pending removal request found for this item.'=>'No pending removal request found for this item.','The removal link has expi