ing on the main Agnosis site.','block keywordartist'=>'artist','block keywordbreadcrumb'=>'breadcrumb','block keywordsubdomain'=>'subdomain','block keywordagnosis'=>'agnosis','block titleArtist Name Link'=>'Artist Name Link','block descriptionLinks to the current artist\'s own subdomain home. Renders nothing off an artist subdomain.'=>'Links to the current artist\'s own subdomain home. Renders nothing off an artist subdomain.','block titleBreadcrumb Icon Link'=>'Breadcrumb Icon Link','block descriptionA single icon-only link (Biography, Events, or a Contact popover) to/about the current artist. Renders nothing if there\'s nothing to show (no biography/events yet, or the artist has turned contact off), or off an artist subdomain.'=>'A single icon-only link (Biography, Events, or a Contact popover) to/about the current artist. Renders nothing if there\'s nothing to show (no biography/events yet, or the artist has turned contact off), or off an artist subdomain.','block keywordbiography'=>'biography','block keywordevents'=>'events','block keywordcontact'=>'contact','block keywordicon'=>'icon','block titleArtist Contact Form'=>'Artist Contact Form','block descriptionContact form letting a visitor message the current artist subdomain\'s artist. Submits to a per-artist REST endpoint; the message is moderated, translated into the artist\'s own language, and emailed to them.'=>'Contact form letting a visitor message the current artist subdomain\'s artist. Submits to a per-artist REST endpoint; the message is moderated, translated into the artist\'s own language, and emailed to them.','block keywordmessage'=>'message','block keywordemail'=>'email','block titleAgnosis Gallery Overview'=>'Agnosis Gallery Overview','block descriptionProportional, randomized artwork grid across all artists. Shows featured artworks first, respects per-artist budget, supports medium filtering and pagination.'=>'Proportional, randomised artwork grid across all artists. Shows featured artworks first, respects per-artist budget, supports medium filtering and pagination.','block keywordgallery'=>'gallery','block keywordartwork'=>'artwork','block keywordartists'=>'artists','block keywordoverview'=>'overview','block titleJoin Agnosis'=>'Join Agnosis','block descriptionPublic application form for artists who want to join the Agnosis network. Submits to the admission REST endpoint. Place this on your /join/ page.'=>'Public application form for artists who want to join the Agnosis network. Submits to the admission REST endpoint. Place this on your /join/ page.','block keywordjoin'=>'join','block keywordapply'=>'apply','block keywordapplication'=>'application','block keywordadmission'=>'admission','block titleNewsletter Popover'=>'Newsletter Popover','block descriptionIcon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled (Settings → Newsletter).'=>'Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled (Settings → Newsletter).','block keywordnewsletter'=>'newsletter','block keywordsubscribe'=>'subscribe','block keywordpopover'=>'popover','block keywordfooter'=>'footer','block titleNewsletter Signup'=>'Newsletter Signup','block descriptionEmail signup form for the public newsletter (double opt-in). Submits to the newsletter subscribe REST endpoint.'=>'Email signup form for the public newsletter (double opt-in). Submits to the newsletter subscribe REST endpoint.','block keywordsignup'=>'signup','block titleMy Submissions'=>'My Submissions','block descriptionLists the logged-in artist\'s pending artwork submissions for review and approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor template.'=>'Lists the logged-in artist\'s pending artwork submissions for review and approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor template.','block keywordsubmissions'=>'submissions','block keywordreview'=>'review','Sensitive by default'=>'Sensitive by default','Mark artworks under this medium as sensitive content by default'=>'Mark artworks under this medium as sensitive content by default','Federated posts under this medium will carry a content warning on the Fediverse (e.g. Mastodon) unless the artist turns it off for a specific piece.'=>'Federated posts under this medium will carry a content warning on the Fediverse (e.g. Mastodon) unless the artist turns it off for a specific piece.','Sensitive content'=>'Sensitive content','Signature must cover the Date header.'=>'Signature must cover the Date header.','Signature on a POST request must cover the Digest header.'=>'Signature on a POST request must cover the Digest header.','Actor document could not be fetched (cached failure).'=>'Actor document could not be fetched (cached failure).','No such artist actor.'=>'No such artist actor.']];